10 June 2009All media are invited to a briefing by the Deputy President of the Republic, Mr Kgalema Motlanthe, on the country's state of readiness for the 2009 FIFA Confederations Cup. Prior to the briefing, Deputy President Motlanthe will convene a meeting of the 2010 Inter-Ministerial Committee, where he will receive reports from concerned departments on the country's state of readiness for the 2009 FIFA Confederations Cup.The briefing will be held as follows:Date: 10 June 2009 Time: 16h00 Venue: Tuynhuys, Cape TownFor more information contact : Tiyani Rikhotso Cell: 083 800 9936 E-mail: tiyani@gcis.gov.zaIssued by: Government Communications (GCIS)